{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Klings KUNGS/ \nkas tohs J̧sdſichts no Israēta \nfapulzina/ fatka: Es fapulzina- \nfchu pee winna wehl wairak/pee \nteem/ kas pee winna jaw fapul- \nzinati irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſi juhs Swehri Lanká \nnahzeet ehſt/ ir wiſſi juhs Sweh- \nri Meschâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſi winnu Sargi irr \nakli/ tee ne finn ueneeka/ tee irr \nwiſſi mehmi Sunni/ kas reet ne \nmahſ/ tee irr Snauschi/ apgl- \nlahs/ eemihl to Meegu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ſcheem Sunneem irr \napreppchts Prahts/ ka tee ne \nwarr pee-eḥdinati tapt. Ir tee \nGanni/ kas paſchi ne mahk fa- \nprasi/ tee wiſſi greeschahs us fa- \nweem Zelkeem/ ikweens us fawn \nNegautibu dohdahs fawa Dsih- \niotchana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nahzeet tchurp / (fatka \ntee:) Es dabbufchu Wihnu/ un \nnehs gribbam stipru Dsehreenu \nſert/ un ta Rihta Deena buhs \na ſchodeen/ ir ſeelaka un tohti \nabbaka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Taifnajs eet bohjâ/ \nin neweens irr/ kas to pee Šîrds \njeemm/ un tee ſwehti Laudis tohp \nobſtremti/ un neweens leek to \nvehra. Jo tas Taifnajs tohp \nobſtjemts preeſch Launuma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas fawa Taifntbâ irr \nfaigajſchi/ nahſ pee Meera/ un \ndufs fawds Rainbaros.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta LVII. Nodalla. \nMahziba/ ko buhs turreht no ta/ kad tee ſwehti\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Laudis apmirſt: r. Teem Judeēin koſp \nweena Sohdiba fluddinata winro Eikadee. \nwibas pehz: z. Eepree zinaschana preeſch \nteem/ kam ſagrausta un apbehdinata Girds \nirraid: 13. etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Omebr ateitta juhs \nſlaht/ juhs Behrni tahs \nSihmeezes/ tu Paulibas \npahrkahpigs Dsimmmuns / un \nkas juhs Mauzibu dsennat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pahr ko juhs nu preeza- \nfeeteeg? prett ko juhs fawu Mut- \nti platti atplehtifeet / un fawn \nMehli garri iſkahrſeet ? Woj juhs \nne effat pahrkahpigi Behrni/ un \nwiltigs Dsimmmuns?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas juhs fakarſtat Ohſolu \nKruhmōs/ appakſch wiſſeem fat- \nteem Kohkeem/ un nokaujat tohs \nBehrnus pee tahm Uppehm/ap- \npakſch to Aknixa-Kalnu Stuh- \nreem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pee teem gtuddeneim Up- \npes Aknineem irr tawa Dalta/ \ntee irr tawa Teefa/ un teem is- \ngahſ tn Dseraimo-Uppuri / tu \nuppure Ehdamo-Uppuri/ woj es \nvahr to liſchohs eepreezinateeſ?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu taiſi tawn Gultu us \nweenu leeſu un angstu Kalun/ir \ntur tu uskahp uppurns uppu- \nreht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pakkat tahm Durwin \nun Stendereim eezell tu tawu \nPeeminneſchann / jo tu atſah- \njees no mannim/ un uskahp/ tu \niſpletti tawu Gultu platti / un \ndarri weenu Derribu ar teem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu mihle winno Gultu \niebnrrā Weetā/ fo tu eeraugi. \nTu eij ar Etji pee ta Rehnina/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
